com.edugility.jpa.converters

Class BooleanToShortConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edugility.jpa.converters.BooleanToShortConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeConverter<Boolean,Short>

    public class BooleanToShortConverter
extends Object
implements AttributeConverter<Boolean,Short>
    An AttributeConverter that converts a Boolean to and from a Short representation.

    This AttributeConverter is used mostly to map the Java Boolean type to a database type of TINYINT, following the recommened JDBC type mapping of TINYINT to short.

    Author:
    Laird Nelson

      • convertToEntityAttribute

        public Boolean convertToEntityAttribute(Short s)
        Returns a Boolean representing the supplied Short.

        This method may return null.

        If the supplied Short is null, then null will be returned.

        If the supplied Short's value is greater than 0, then Boolean.TRUE will be returned.

        In all other cases, Boolean.FALSE will be returned.

        Specified by:
        convertToEntityAttribute in interface AttributeConverter<Boolean,Short>
        Parameters:
        s - the Short to convert; may be null in which case null will be returned
        Returns:
        null if s is null, Boolean.TRUE if s's value is greater than 0, or Boolean.FALSE in all other cases className}
